text: Kristina Karapetan (born 3 August 1992 in Chara, Kalarsky District) is a Kazakhstani female volleyball player. She was a member of the Kazakhstan women's national volleyball team at the 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship. She played for Irtysh Kazchrome in 2018. == References == ==Other websites == *kristina-karapetian globalsportsarchive.com Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani volleyball players
